  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Building resilience through solar ovens in Bolivia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This package is to manage income for the Building Resilience and improving quality of life of Amazonian Communities in Bolivia with Solar Ovens project, which will provide 100 families in the Amazon with solar ovens to improve their resilience. This is a three year project, scaling up activities from a pilot carried out in 2015. There is a second Package for this project -PP0368 &apos;Caring for Mother Earth Bolivia&apos;. This package is for the balance of funds to be secured.</narrative>
  </description>
